Stepping into September…♡

This month whispers a flow of transition, of change, of a clearing and reorganisation.
 
Of highlighting our priorities and stripping away the rest. 

Of reflection – a sacred ‘pause’ where we are guided to look around at our lives, look within at who we are, review our course, and decide if we are heading in a direction we desire.
 
Stepping into the month we have the Sun in Virgo.

Virgo reorganises. It is deeply healing, able to place things in their most optimal spaces.

Able to see what is in alignment, and what is ready to fall away.

Being a mutable energy, it speaks to adaptability, flexibility, transition.
 
With our beautiful New Moon in Virgo and an emotional and healing Pisces Full Moon, this month also holds a beautiful event – the September Equinox.

The official halfway point of the astrological year and a harmonious shift in energy as the Sun moves into Libra.
 
Reaching the end of September, we meet the last  Mercury Retrograde of 2021, bringing us to a total of 6 planets in retrograde for a moment.

This cosmic line up of our beautiful planets moving in a retrograde emphasises that sacred pause, reflection, introspection, and review of our lives.

With the numerology of both 5 and 9, this shows us both changes in direction and endings of a cycle.

September’s full energetic report can be found inside our Flow with the Moon Membership.

With the key astrological transits of the month and their dates, with a dive into each New and Full Moon, and an in-depth tarot reading covering the energy.

This month inside of the membership, we have a New Moon Ritual with the beautiful @tanya_saunders_ – a healing breathwork session.

We also dive into the final Mercury Retrograde of 2021, and the beautiful September Equinox.

Along with a beautiful tarot reading for the month, intention setting, soul prompts, gratitude work and more.
